TEST authenticate_user_invalid_token

RECEIVE HTTP:GET /api/v1/users/auth
HEADERS
  Authorization: Bearer invalid_token_xyz

EXPECT READ:MYSQL users
USING_SQL """
SELECT * FROM `users` WHERE `users`.`token` = 'invalid_token_xyz' LIMIT 1
"""
RETURNS EMPTY

RESPOND HTTP:401
WITH {{payloads/auth_error_response.json}}
